#+title:   Supported classes
#+date:    {{ date }}
#+startup: content

* Overview
Winnow recognizes *{{ exact-count }}* exact matches and *{{ prefix-count }}* prefix patterns.

- Exact matches: Classes like =block=, =hidden=, =flex= that match exactly
- Prefix patterns: Patterns like =p-*=, =bg-*= that match any suffix

* Exact Matches
These classes are recognized exactly as written.
{% for group in exact-groups %}
** {{ group.name }}
{% for class in group.classes %}- ~{{ class }}~
{% endfor %}{% endfor %}
* Prefix Patterns
These patterns match =<prefix>-<value>=. For example, =p-*= matches =p-4=, =p-px=, =p-[10px]=.

{% for prefix in prefixes %}- ~{{ prefix }}-*~
{% endfor %}
* Colors
These color names are recognized in color utilities like =bg-*=, =text-*=, =border-*=.

{% for color in colors %}- ~{{ color }}~
{% endfor %}
